Coke studio going high… season after season… What a marvelous compilation… excellent team work. I’m sure this one would go into the heart of millions… Sincere thanks, and hearty contras to the whole team.  Just one word, It starts with an Aya from Quran in which it is recited as `Arrahmanu Rahim’ but the correct way to recite is `Arrahmani Rahim’ 

بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ
